'“I have no objection to investigating,” I said, “but I doubt that we shall find a friend if we find the author.”',
'“It is most mystifying,” said Pan Dan Chee.',
'“All my life I have believed, as all other inhabitants of Horz have believed, that the pits of Horz were deserted.',
