'We shall be great friends.',
'You shall stay here with me forever, as all the countless others have.',
'I shall have company in the lonely pits of Horz.”',
'Then he laughed maniacally.',
'It was evident that the creature was quite mad.',
'He not only looked it, he acted it.',
'Sometimes his speech was inarticulate gibber; often it was broken by meaningless and inopportune laughter—the hollow laugh that we had heard before.',
'His appearance was most repulsive.',
'He was naked except for the harness which supported a sword and a dagger, and the skin of his malformed body was a ghastly white—the color of a corpse.',
'His flabby mouth hung open, revealing a few yellow, snaggled fangs.',
'His eyes were wide and round, the whites showing entirely around the irises.',
'He had no nose; it appeared to have been eaten away by disease.',
'I kept my eye on him constantly while Pan Dan Chee drank; then he watched him while I slaked my thirst, and all the while the creature kept up a running fire of senseless chatter.',
